data.title: Un Couple [A Couple] (Three original photographs of Jean-Pierre Mocky and Juliette Mayniel on the set of the 1960 film) by Jean-Pierre Mocky (director, screenwriter); Raymond Queneau, Alain Moury, Jac
data.meta_description: Balzac, Paris - 1960 - Three vintage borderless reference photographs from the set of the 1960 French film, showing director Jean-Pierre Mocky, actors Juliette Mayniel, Jean Kosta, and other members of the cast and crew. With numbered stamps on the verso. A husband and wife decide to separate when they realize their relationship lacks sexual excitement after three years together. Shot on location in France. 6.75 x 5.5 inches. About Near Fine. - Un Couple [A Couple] (Three original photographs of Jean-Pierre Mocky and Juliette Mayniel on the set of the 1960 film)
